{"id":11866,"date":"2020-08-31T07:45:52","date_gmt":"2020-08-31T07:45:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/?page_id=11866"},"modified":"2021-05-17T09:42:52","modified_gmt":"2021-05-17T09:42:52","slug":"elaboration-des-normes","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/normalisation\/elaboration-des-normes\/","title":{"rendered":"\u00c9laboration des Normes"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"limit-wrapper\"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  wpv-first-level first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-ad1ce959ebb0eb7519b6faee55bb4359\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-3307c66878e32015de187cb935356961\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-42e63e3427a9546f05d092d899c03a73\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-e8b589ffe58d870e1ef233690719c022\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"first\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"250\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme-600x150.jpg 600w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme-300x75.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme-768x192.jpg 768w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme-800x200.jpg 800w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme-555x139.jpg 555w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme-360x90.jpg 360w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/elabornorme-262x66.jpg 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>QUI \u00c9LABORE LES NORMES GABONAISES ?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Les normes Gabonaises\u00a0 sont examin\u00e9es et \u00e9labor\u00e9es au sein <a href=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/normalisation\/comite-technique-de-la-normalisation\/\"><strong>des comit\u00e9s techniques (CT) de normalisation<\/strong><\/a> qui sont compos\u00e9es des repr\u00e9sentants suivants\u00a0:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Administrations et \u00e9tablissements publics concern\u00e9s par le secteur en question\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li>Fabricants, prestataires de service\u00a0ou\/et leurs organisations repr\u00e9sentatives ;<\/li>\n<li>Organismes d\u2019\u00e9valuation de la conformit\u00e9\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li>Etablissements de recherche et de formation\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li>Consommateurs ou utilisateurs\u00a0;<\/li>\n<li>Organisations non gouvernementales\u00a0ou syndicales.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-4e84fea5f350ea9d3160090d9af24891\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>PROCESSUS D&rsquo;\u00c9LABORATION DES NORMES GABONAISES<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright wp-image-11974 size-medium\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-293x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"293\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-293x300.png 293w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-600x615.png 600w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-768x787.png 768w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-60x60.png 60w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-43x43.png 43w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-800x820.png 800w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-555x569.png 555w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-360x369.png 360w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor-262x269.png 262w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/gagafor.png 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 293px) 100vw, 293px\" \/>La Normalisation est une activit\u00e9 qui vise l\u2019\u00e9laboration des normes dans tous les secteurs d\u2019activit\u00e9s dans\u00a0 un contexte \u00a0faisant intervenir toutes les parties int\u00e9ress\u00e9es.<\/p>\n<p>Les normes adopt\u00e9es selon une proc\u00e9dure faisant appel au consensus, sont des documents contenant des sp\u00e9cifications techniques ou autres crit\u00e8res pr\u00e9cis destin\u00e9s \u00e0 \u00eatre utilis\u00e9s en tant que r\u00e8gles ou lignes directrices pour assurer que des mat\u00e9riaux, produits, syst\u00e8mes, processus et services sont aptes \u00e0 leur emploi.<\/p>\n<p>Les normes examin\u00e9es et adopt\u00e9es dans un cadre regroupant toutes les parties concern\u00e9es sont valid\u00e9es par une enqu\u00eate publique permettant de s\u2019assurer que les normes correspondent \u00e0 l\u2019int\u00e9r\u00eat g\u00e9n\u00e9ral.<\/p>\n<p>Les normes contribuent \u00e0 simplifier et \u00e0 accro\u00eetre la fiabilit\u00e9 et l\u2019efficacit\u00e9 des biens et services et constituent les r\u00e9f\u00e9rentiels de base pour tout syst\u00e8me de certification et un outil incontestable pour le contr\u00f4le de la qualit\u00e9 et de la s\u00e9curit\u00e9 des produits et services.<\/p>\n<p>Les normes sont soumises \u00e0 un m\u00e9canisme d\u2019actualisation leur permettant de refl\u00e9ter en permanence l\u2019\u00e9tat de la technologie et de constituer un outil indispensable pour l\u2019am\u00e9lioration des exportations et la protection des consommateurs.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":11851,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11866"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11866"}],"version-history":[{"count":19,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11866\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":13977,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11866\/revisions\/13977"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11851"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11866"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}